{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bdbeb02d0b","title":"周恩来对驻合肥的第十二军军长李德生的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3ed9dce106","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"bdbeb02d0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"f3ee2f4a99","name":"李德生","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0fe2148733","type":"title","text":"周恩来对驻合肥的第十二军军长李德生的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bdbeb02d0b"},{"id":"562eb4c426","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bdbeb02d0b"},{"id":"e5100cb4d1","type":"paragraph","text":"（李德生报告：一群人大闹军管会半个多月，冲砸军部，打伤军首长。部队劝说无效。怎么办？）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bdbeb02d0b"},{"id":"606ad9a34e","type":"paragraph","text":"以电话告李军长，先进行政治工作；不听，宣布“九五”命令，进行分化，要他们交出祸首、凶手；再不听，待其直接行凶，当场将凶手逮捕。对胁从者晓以大义，宣布一律不究，但如再犯，仍将当场逮捕凶手、祸首。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bdbeb02d0b"}],"page":{"id":"eff0ed7cb8","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"bdbeb02d0b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}